{"tid":1432903,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"抗爭向暴力升級，你便墮入建制的把戲內。當權者會不惜一切地惹怒你","createTime":"2019-08-08T10:53:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-09T03:14:25.000Z","uid":201732,"like":7,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"86c68d5d37423e634055d42afd8dcdbd4d2b55f4","tid":1432903,"uid":201732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T10:53:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AHEAVER.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAHEAVER.jpg&h=e68ca2aa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我地要be water，佢係要定性你做暴徒，偏偏你地和平抗爭幾個月，佢冇回應，你再升級，再次同大眾講，係當權者迫民眾架！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">89，810，811和你飛</span>"},{"pid":"d153f2bc158b753ca94500901ec5761cf348a862","tid":1432903,"uid":201732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T10:58:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ba1d88346b420161eb7040113db64da20bbc1a1","tid":1432903,"uid":201732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T11:26:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QXUJkit.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQXUJkit.jpg&h=ddd1414a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"996b452a22b915f290637c42b20c972d43bdecfc","tid":1432903,"uid":55384,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T11:49:39.000Z","msg":"不割席,但係而家的確要和理非入場,對面玩抹黑<br />\n勇武要休息一陣先"},{"pid":"fe946aad095db5299d554615c5890362e9e46a0d","tid":1432903,"uid":69473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T11:58:06.000Z","msg":"香港人團結加油<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">我哋無退路，退一步唔係海闊天空，唔係袋住先<br />\n而係新疆集中營，全香港監控燈柱</span><br />\n<br />\n我哋會羸，一定要羸<br />\n五大訴求，缺一不可<br />\n<br />\n爭你一個爭好遠<br />\n多你一個幫到好多<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>我哋會有一日係煲底下面，夏愨道，警總，立法會門口，大家除低口罩，頭盔，真真正正係度野餐<br />\n<br />\n天佑香港，香港人要羸返香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span>"},{"pid":"d